OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScientists help save UK    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpint from climate change   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scientists fear climate change could   
OL,6, "call time" on the great British pint  
OL,7, and are helping the brewing industry to
OL,8, save it.                               
OL,10,FHops give bitter its taste but the     
OL,11,Fplant doesn't like the hotter, drier   
OL,12,Fconditions we've experienced in recent 
OL,13,Fdecades and production has plummeted.  
OL,15,FResearchers in Kent are isolating hop  
OL,16,Fgenes in the hope of producing more    
OL,17,Fclimate-change resilient varieties.    
OL,19,FThey also want to produce more intense 
OL,20,Fflavours that are now becoming popular.
